</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/bonome" rel="author">bonome</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-01-21T09:03:05+01:00"><span class="date">le 21/01/13</span> <span class="time">à 09:03</span></time>.
